data.value: SELECT scoreTable.sessionID, scoreTable.classID, scoreTable.studentFullName, stdClassTable.stdClass, subjectTable.subjectName, subjectTable.subjectTeacherName, subjectTable.subjectID FROM studentTable INNER JOIN ((scoreTable INNER JOIN subjectTable ON (scoreTable.sessionID = subjectTable.sessionID) AND (scoreTable.classID = subjectTable.classID) AND (scoreTable.subjectID = subjectTable.subjectID)) INNER JOIN stdClassTable ON scoreTable.classID = stdClassTable.classID) ON (scoreTable.sessionID = studentTable.sessionID) AND (studentTable.stdID = scoreTable.stdID);
